{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "I don't know every train or every second-- I mean every box or every second car, there was like a little [NON-ENGLISH], like a little [NON-ENGLISH] where the soldier was standing up, you know, in the train.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "He was standing up where he could have a view.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Every few cars had like a soldier was there, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And that's all you heard in the train, going, go, go, go, go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Even today, whenever I travel a train, you know-- pop, pop, pop-- that's the first thing that comes back to my mind is-- is-- is-- is the-- is the railroad.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "It was going until the next day around the afternoon we reached the place that must have been Slovakia, Slovakia, because I pulled myself up and I saw people which were not Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And the fields were beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "This was in May, late May.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Countryside was gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the elderly people in the car would say, which way are we going?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somebody said, we are heading north.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then someone says, if we are heading north, we're in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we are heading towards Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want you to know that we were in Hungary until 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We still didn't know what the Holocaust-- the Holocaust was going full blast in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Millions of Jews were killed in Russia, the Ukraine, France, all the occupied countries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hungary was the last country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My village, the Russians were in my village that October.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only six months prior to that, the Russians already were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the last action of the Germans during World War II.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They lost the war already.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
